column5: Fished the Niagara Friday and today and managed to do quite well, although today was pretty cold with the wind chill! Here's one of a bunch landed over the last 2 trips
WTG man... Healthy looking steelie too...
Great colours!  Great fish!  Great pic!  Nice work out there...esp with the wind and cold.
WTG Nice reward for braving the elements  TB
Right on, nice to see for sure.  Good for you!  Joey
